{"vocabInfos":[{"lsjDefs":"<b> ἀπο-σχίζω</b>, <br /> <b>split, cleave off,</b> ἀπὸ δ᾽ ἔσχισεν αὐτήν [τὴν πέτρην] [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 8th c.BC: Odyssea Homerus Epicus “Odyssey” 4.507\">Refs 8th c.BC+</a>]; <b>tear off,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Euripides Tragicus “Alcestis” 172, 2nd-3rd c.AD: Oppianus Anazarbensis Epicus “Halieutica - Poetae Bucolici et Didactici” 2.623. \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__2</b></Level3> <b>sever, detach from,</b> τινὰ ἀπὸ τοῦ συμμαχικοῦ[<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Herodotus Historicus 6.9\">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; ἀ. Αυδούς <b>part</b> them <b>off, separate</b> them, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th-6th c.BC: Plato Philosophus “Politicus” 262e; τὴν ἰδίαν ψυχὴν τῆς τῶν λογικῶν 2nd c.AD: Marcus Antoninus Imperator 4.29:\">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>] — <i>passive</i>, ἀποσχισθῆναι ἀπό.., of a river <b>being parted from</b> the main stream, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Herodotus Historicus 2.17, 4.56 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; of a tribe <b>detached from</b> its parent stock, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] 1.58, 143; ἀπὸ τῆς μεγάλης φλεβὸς -σχίζεται 4th c.BC: Aristoteles Philosophus “Historia Animalium” 514b10: with _genitive_, ἀποσχισθέντες τῆς ἄλλης στρατιῆς 5th c.BC: Herodotus Historicus 8.35, compare 7.233, 5th-6th c.BC: Plato Philosophus “Politicus” 267b, etc.\">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]:—<i>middle</i>, <b>separate oneself,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] “Lg.” 728b; τοῦ σοφιστοῦ 4th c.AD: Libanius Sophista “Orationes” 3.24. \">Refs 4th c.AD+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__3</b></Level3> <i>metaphorically</i>, ἀ. τινὰ τοῦ λόγου <b>cut</b> him <b>off from</b> his speech, <b>interrupt</b> him <b>in</b> it, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th-6th c.BC: Aristophanes Comicus “Nubes” 1408.\">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]","strongNumber":"G6498","accentedUnicode":"ἀποσχίζω","shortDef":"to sever","mediumDef":"to sever","stepGloss":"to sever","stepTransliteration":"aposchizō","count":0,"_step_Type":"verb"}]}